The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, surfing, basketball
1. the person drinking cola is not the fan of reggae##6
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the fan of blues##7
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the fan of country and the person drinking fanta##7
5. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is surfing is the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the fan of blues is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | cola | iced-tea | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | d&b  | country  | blues    |
| Sport           | basketball | swimming  | lacrosse    | surfing    |

