The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, magic-tricks, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: british, chinese, colombian, egyptian
1. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
8. the person watching epic movies is not the british##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre      | western     | epic | mystery        | satire       |
