3. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is photography##2
4. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
5. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
7. the musician is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the airplane##7
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
