4 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, fish, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, skateboard, tram
 1. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the fish##2
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the owner of the hamster is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | sprite     | fanta      | milk     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig  | hamster   | mouse   | fish |
| Transport     | tram     | helicopter | skateboard | roller   |

