There are 4 different favourite colors: green, black, white, apricot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who likes apricot##7
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who likes black##7
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
4. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
5. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who likes green##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
8. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who likes green##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | cucumber | corn          | carrot  |
| Color   | white    | green      | black    | apricot   |
| Sport         | parkour | cycling  | skateboarding | surfing |

